        question: "How is co-hosting different from full-service management?",
        answer: "With co-hosting, you maintain ownership of your Airbnb listing, account, and Superhost status. You receive payouts directly from Airbnb, and we invoice you monthly for our services. With full-service management, we control the listing and handle all financials. Co-hosting is perfect if you want to maintain your host profile while getting professional support."
