      {
        question: "Can I maintain my Superhost status with a co-host?",
        answer: "Absolutely! Since the listing stays under your account, all positive reviews and ratings contribute to your Superhost status. Our professional service actually helps you achieve and maintain Superhost by ensuring consistently excellent guest experiences."
      },
